One of his stupid models, yeah.

19:26.160 --> 19:29.560
It's very good. I didn't say
he wasn't good at models.

19:31.240 --> 19:33.040
Hello? Hello there?

19:33.040 --> 19:35.360
I got your apology!

19:35.360 --> 19:37.200
I have a pie!

19:37.200 --> 19:39.160
I don't understand.

19:39.160 --> 19:42.120
If he was that bad for
all those years... No.

19:42.120 --> 19:44.240
..why didn't you just...?
No, I know.

19:44.240 --> 19:46.960
I had a chance of pushing him down
a huge flight of stairs

19:46.960 --> 19:49.320
a few years ago,
but chickened out last minute.

19:49.320 --> 19:52.840
No! I don't mean
why didn't you kill him sooner.

19:52.840 --> 19:55.280
I mean, why didn't you
just leave him?

19:55.280 --> 19:59.160
Hello! I've accepted your apology!

19:59.160 --> 20:02.040
Sunk cost fallacy.

20:02.040 --> 20:05.280
What? It's a term I learned
at business school

20:05.280 --> 20:07.320
when I had my own ambitions...

20:07.320 --> 20:09.520
..and before I gave my life to him.

20:09.520 --> 20:10.840
Well, what does it mean?

20:10.840 --> 20:12.480
Hello?

20:12.480 --> 20:14.680
What does it matter?
It's over now.

20:16.080 --> 20:17.520
Do what you need to do.

20:19.040 --> 20:20.920
Anyway...

20:20.920 --> 20:22.640
..you wouldn't understand.

20:22.640 --> 20:24.560
Hello?

20:34.880 --> 20:36.960
Ahh!

20:42.320 --> 20:44.000
Try me.

20:45.920 --> 20:47.360
Can I show you something?

20:58.560 --> 20:59.760
Where are we going?

20:59.760 --> 21:02.440
Have you ever heard of
the Dolomites? Yes, of course.

21:02.440 --> 21:05.080
It's where the castle is
with the man, isn't it?

21:05.080 --> 21:07.200
Yeah. No, 'course you haven't.

21:07.200 --> 21:09.440
It's a mountain range in Italy.

21:09.440 --> 21:11.840
My grandfather,
he was from the region,

21:11.840 --> 21:13.240
and when I was a little girl,

21:13.240 --> 21:16.200
he used to tell me tales
of their beauty.

21:16.200 --> 21:17.920
Crystal-clear lakes.

21:17.920 --> 21:21.520
Air so pure, you'd feel drunk
with every inhalation.

21:21.520 --> 21:23.520
Erm, around every corner,

21:23.520 --> 21:25.640
a more godlike vista.

21:25.640 --> 21:29.200
Anyway, in the months leading up
to my 50th birthday,

21:29.200 --> 21:30.800
I dropped so many hints -

21:30.800 --> 21:33.760
my longing to go there,
to breathe in that air.

21:33.760 --> 21:35.240
I even took Italian lessons.

21:35.240 --> 21:36.680
And...

21:43.320 --> 21:44.800
Oh, God.

21:47.600 --> 21:50.240
Yeah.

21:58.680 --> 22:00.040
It took him months.

22:00.040 --> 22:01.480
Barely saw him.

22:01.480 --> 22:03.120
He'd creep into bed at night.

22:03.120 --> 22:05.200
The stench of glue will
haunt me for life.

22:05.200 --> 22:06.800
Well, it's sort of sweet.

22:06.800 --> 22:08.800
He remembered you liked
the Dolomites.

22:08.800 --> 22:11.720
What? Well, it shows
he was listening, doesn't it?

22:11.720 --> 22:13.920
Hey, for my mum's
birthday this year,

22:13.920 --> 22:15.440
my dad bought her a telescope.

22:15.440 --> 22:17.000
She's registered blind.

22:18.760 --> 22:20.840
A lifetime following him around

22:20.840 --> 22:24.080
from model convention
to miniature railway.

22:24.080 --> 22:26.880
And the one chance
that he has to make up

22:26.880 --> 22:29.440
for 35 years of disappointment

22:29.440 --> 22:31.800
and take me to the place
of my dreams...

22:31.800 --> 22:33.400
..and he makes me a model of it?!

22:34.840 --> 22:38.080
No! This is all about him.

22:38.080 --> 22:41.600
And, anyway, I want to live life.

22:41.600 --> 22:46.680
I don't want to stare at
a mini polystyrene version of it.

22:46.680 --> 22:48.960
You married a nerd!

22:48.960 --> 22:50.960
Why did you stay with a nerd?

22:50.960 --> 22:53.280
Sunk cost fallacy, I told you.

22:53.280 --> 22:56.120
If you invest a lifetime
into something,

22:56.120 --> 23:00.040
pulling out means
that lifetime meant nothing.

23:00.040 --> 23:02.480
Fine. Why did you have to stab him?

23:02.480 --> 23:04.320
Because I loved him.

23:05.800 --> 23:08.440
OK, you're an absolute nut job.

23:08.440 --> 23:09.880
Maybe.

23:09.880 --> 23:12.280
Well, you're not going
to get away with it.

23:12.280 --> 23:14.360
There'll be pictures
of you everywhere.

23:14.360 --> 23:16.680
Oh, I've no intention of
getting away with it.

23:19.240 --> 23:20.520
Tea?

23:25.400 --> 23:26.440
Oh...

23:26.440 --> 23:27.800
Ah!

23:29.520 --> 23:31.360
I think you should turn yourself in.

23:31.360 --> 23:32.760
Oh, I agree. You do?

23:32.760 --> 23:34.400
Oh, yes. Bourbon?

23:35.840 --> 23:37.960
Yeah.

23:37.960 --> 23:40.920
I mean, I could put a pretty
strong argument together

23:40.920 --> 23:42.640
for why I cracked,

23:42.640 --> 23:45.600
but, no, that's not my intention.

23:45.600 --> 23:48.560
I committed an awful crime...

23:48.560 --> 23:50.960
..and I must pay the price.

23:50.960 --> 23:53.560
Fine. So what's with
all the packing, then?

23:53.560 --> 23:57.680
Are they having pool parties
in prison now? Well...

23:57.680 --> 24:00.800
..since he died, I feel amazing.

24:00.800 --> 24:02.840
I see beauty everywhere.

24:02.840 --> 24:04.640
I feel reborn.

24:04.640 --> 24:06.960
So, no, I must go to prison,

24:06.960 --> 24:10.240
I know I must, but before that...

24:10.240 --> 24:12.360
Well, I had wanted to go there.

24:12.360 --> 24:14.040
To go where?

24:14.040 --> 24:15.320
Dolomites!

24:16.440 --> 24:19.440
I wanted to breathe in that air

24:19.440 --> 24:21.040
and swim in those waters,

24:21.040 --> 24:25.280
and feel for once, just once,
I wanted to feel alive.

24:25.280 --> 24:29.600
In the moment -
no past, no future, just alive.

24:29.600 --> 24:33.680
Just two weeks of pure freedom.

24:33.680 --> 24:37.160
Cold gelato. Dry white wine.

24:37.160 --> 24:41.600
Eating lemons directly off the tree.

24:41.600 --> 24:43.760
Oh...yes.

24:43.760 --> 24:45.360
That does sound good.

24:46.560 --> 24:49.480
