eating lemons.

24:49.480 --> 24:51.360
Come with me. What?!

24:51.360 --> 24:53.040
Come with me. Oh, you're...

24:53.040 --> 24:54.560
Crazy. Yeah. I know.

24:54.560 --> 24:56.440
Why would you want me
to come with you?

24:56.440 --> 24:58.880
Oh, don't flatter yourself.
You're not my type.

24:58.880 --> 25:00.840
Your life is going nowhere.

25:00.840 --> 25:03.200
You're a single 50-year-old man,
no children,

25:03.200 --> 25:05.320
