25:05.320 --> 25:07.200
I'm very good at my job!

25:07.200 --> 25:10.320
I'm actually seeing
a tattooed milf, so...

25:10.320 --> 25:11.720
Oh...

25:11.720 --> 25:13.080
Oh, God.

25:13.080 --> 25:17.080
Tell me one thing you've got
to look forward to. Just one.

25:17.080 --> 25:19.280
Me and the lads are going
to see Slack Sabbath.

25:19.280 --> 25:22.400
Black Sabbath?
No, they're like them, but...

25:22.400 --> 25:25.040
..they're fat.

25:25.040 --> 25:26.680
Live.

25:26.680 --> 25:28.640
Live for once.

25:30.440 --> 25:32.040
All right.

25:32.040 --> 25:33.400
I will. Sod it.

25:33.400 --> 25:35.480
Really? Yeah. Why not?

25:35.480 --> 25:37.000
The tattooed milf'll keep.

25:37.000 --> 25:38.880
Oh, my God!

25:38.880 --> 25:42.080
Oh, my God. Erm... I'll just
get the rest of my things.

25:42.080 --> 25:43.440
You'll need some clothes.

25:43.440 --> 25:45.400
Shall I, uh, drop you off
at your place?

25:45.400 --> 25:48.080
We'll take my van. They won't have
put a port check on that yet.

25:48.080 --> 25:50.680
Good thinking.
I hope you like vino bianco!

25:51.720 --> 25:53.400
I'm more of a beer man.

25:53.400 --> 25:55.720
But those Continental lagers
